		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just checked out Tiled and it seems like it would make life so much easier than the way I was doing things IF it could export to SNES specs. Is it possible to use this with the SNES or would a plugin be needed? In the past I played with GBA DEV and it was much easier, but there is somthing about the SNES that just gets me. maybe because when I first played one at a friends house (back when it came out)  I thought it couldn't get ant better <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" />

		

