	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />SNES does not have any special specs for maps, it is purely software thing - i.e. SNES does not handle large level maps automatically. So a plugin would be needed, to export the data into format of your map engine.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


