	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You don't need to use Java to write Tiled plugins (in fact I'd assume those only work with the old Java version of Tiled). Tiled uses XML based file format  for its maps so you can parse them using pretty much any language. The format is documented online.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


